{"tid":1664093,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"入黎睇睇少數族裔手足對我地講嘅野！！！","createTime":"2019-10-19T23:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T05:38:33.000Z","uid":12185,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a8d9d9cc8dcc9719b5fe4c8bfcb989531667a0","tid":1664093,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:43:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警告：催淚，小心食用<br />\n<br />\n由2014雨革去到而家，真正嘅香港民族已經喺社運入面誕生，不論你係咩人、黎自邊度，只要你係一齊為香港嘅價值奮鬥，你就係香港人。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nPinder, 21歲，第三代印度香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Laurel-Chor-HKFP-1-Copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FLaurel-Chor-HKFP-1-Copy.jpg&h=3e3452d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;[During protests] people will say thank you or give me a thumbs-up, but then I don&rsquo;t really know where they are coming from, because I am also part of the community. It is my right to be here and fight for the things I stand for.&rdquo; </span>「手足會走埋黎同我講thank you或者俾個手指公我，但其實我唔明佢地咁做做乜，因為呢度一樣係我屋企。我同你地一樣要行出黎爭取我捍衛嘅野。」<br />\n<br />\nHorjat Grewal, 21歲，香港出世長大<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Laurel-Chor-HKFP-3-Copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FLaurel-Chor-HKFP-3-Copy.jpg&h=5e68e792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;You know, there are not a lot of ethnic minorities showing up, unfortunately, for various reasons. It&rsquo;s disheartening because I want more people to show up and I want more [minorities] to recognise that this is their home, I want more local people to understand that this is our home too, instead of giving us a thumbs-up or saying thanks for being here. No, this is my home, I want to be here.&rdquo;</span><br />\n「唔係好多少數族裔有行出黎。我覺得好失望，因為我想更多人出黎，更加想佢地明白香港係我地大家屋企。我都好想本地人知道香港係我屋企，而唔使俾手指公我或者多謝我。香港係我屋企，我好想留喺度。」<br />\n<br />\nMario, 43歲（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），華人mix菲律賓mix巴基斯坦<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Laurel-Chor-HKFP-4-Copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FLaurel-Chor-HKFP-4-Copy.jpg&h=231be1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;When I was very young, a long time ago in the &rsquo;80s, there was some discrimination. But just look here: we don&rsquo;t care what race you are. [Other protesters] just look at us and they will hand you like a towel and ask: &lsquo;Are you hot? Do you need a mask? Do you need eye protection?&rsquo; People will just help you, they don&rsquo;t care.&rdquo;</span><br />\n「我細個，80年代果陣，啲人係有歧視我地。但你而家睇吓：冇人會理你咩種族。手足只會俾條毛巾我問我熱唔熱，要唔要口罩，要唔要眼罩。佢地唔care架，佢地淨係會幫你。」<br />\n<br />\nAstrid Andersson, 32歲，香港長大<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Laurel-Chor-HKFP-2-Copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FLaurel-Chor-HKFP-2-Copy.jpg&h=83fe3e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;Most people definitely understand that there are also white people, Westerners, that are also Hongkongers. I think that white chicks can get away with a lot of stuff in general, so if there&rsquo;s an opportunity to stand up for what is right in a risky situation &ndash; where it is more risky for other people to do &ndash; then we should do it and we should leverage that privilege, and represent on their behalf, and take advantage of the minimised risk of being white and blonde and a chick.&rdquo;</span><br />\n「好多人都明白其實係有西方黎嘅白人香港人。我覺得白人女性冇咁易出事，所以如果其他人要為左做啱嘅野而承受風險，我地應該運用呢個特權去為佢地爭取。我好樂意用我白人、金髮、女性嘅身份去做呢樣野。」<br />\n<br />\nShak，24歲，香港出世長大<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Laurel-Chor-HKFP-5-Copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FLaurel-Chor-HKFP-5-Copy.jpg&h=fe8d384f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;We&rsquo;re ethnic minorities but we&rsquo;re still Hongkongers at the end of the day. I was born here, I was raised here, I consider myself a Hongkonger. I&rsquo;m not Chinese, but these are all my people at the same time, we&rsquo;re all still fighting the same cause.&quot;</span>「我係少數族裔但我都係香港人。我喺呢度出世，我喺呢度長大，我係香港人。我唔係華裔，但係呢班係我嘅我手足，我地為緊共同嘅理念奮鬥。」<br />\n<br />\nSamir, 23，第三代印度香港人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;Minorities, we&rsquo;re kind of outcasts. We&rsquo;re not Hongkongers, we&rsquo;re not international expats, so we&rsquo;re kind of that middle ground. That&rsquo;s what I appreciate being here [at the protests], it&rsquo;s that everyone is united towards a common goal &ndash; no matter where your ethnic background. We&rsquo;re all unified behind one cause, which is to better Hong Kong.&rdquo;</span><br />\n「我地少數族裔有啲似邊緣人，我地唔係香港人（你地係架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），我地唔係外國僑民，我地有啲似夾左喺中間。呢個係我點解咁鍾意出黎發夢嘅原因，因為我地都係不論種族，為左共同目標而團結。我地都只想做同一樣野，要一個更加好嘅香港。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同場加映：中國大陸手足（真同胞）</strong></span><br />\nBetty Xu, 22歲，因為香港抗爭block左100幾個中國朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://si.wsj.net/public/resources/images/B3-EV123_HKMAIN_M_20190827161343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsi.wsj.net%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fimages%2FB3-EV123_HKMAIN_M_20190827161343.jpg&h=1c0b9444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;m more than before touched by the Hong Kong people, who remained united after so much had happened,&rdquo; Ms. Xu said. &ldquo;That&rsquo;s why I&rsquo;m staying with them.&rdquo;</span><br />\n「香港人令我好感動，經過左咁多野仲咁團結。呢個係我會繼續同佢地同行嘅原因。」"},{"pid":"14c241679590bc91805aab70ef4f890c46f25f08","tid":1664093,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:44:12.000Z","msg":"詳細Source：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/07/06/home-i-want-hong-kongs-ethnic-minority-protesters-identity-belonging/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F07%2F06%2Fhome-i-want-hong-kongs-ethnic-minority-protesters-identity-belonging%2F&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=8b949a7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/07/06/home-i-want-hong-kongs-ethnic-minority-protesters-identity-belonging/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/mainland-chinese-sneak-into-hong-kongs-proteststo-support-the-cause-11566986403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fmainland-chinese-sneak-into-hong-kongs-proteststo-support-the-cause-11566986403&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=67b37f9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/mainland-chinese-sneak-into-hong-kongs-proteststo-support-the-cause-11566986403</a>"},{"pid":"d1bc8707ae9b593470503a2ea9c97738e0be2a98","tid":1664093,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:46:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efa53376ef4b4d95fc730918929e8bd4ba568671","tid":1664093,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6de85ec78c003ece9d6c09f5a0410d72747c1b3","tid":1664093,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c38a1888ca408e06991c53aa149bebaf3db2715","tid":1664093,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:50:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ecd37f722ed04d407f4d44e7933967f67f0ce39","tid":1664093,"uid":79117,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:51:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">They are not fucking minorities, they are Hong Kong citizens as our equals.</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41e28b5942843fef191e3e632e79d1bc35aa349","tid":1664093,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ecd37f722ed04d407f4d44e7933967f67f0ce39","tid":1664093,"uid":79117,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:51:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">They are not fucking minorities, they are Hong Kong citizens as our equals.</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"梁繼平講嘅公民民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3dfbba93e4f4085180858673ccc4a1556c7667","tid":1664093,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017d3e0c331607416fc6edbccee27a7b9a957d7e","tid":1664093,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"大家都係香港人為香港付出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f50c7bdc28fa296294774ccd9072a95ba7b89f","tid":1664093,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4c19cd6652e6cf7243eb9417c3149beb71c53b","tid":1664093,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d335f14c89a6663f2f8af82f8ccb14aeec6bd924","tid":1664093,"uid":1654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"「唔係好多少數族裔有行出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人多就唔係少數啦<br />\n你基數少，出黎梗係少"},{"pid":"425e1dbd954a5f4a67647e24c7dfa36950794c55","tid":1664093,"uid":199902,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"香港人呢個身份從來都唔係以膚色、基因、文化同語言去釐定，只要認同、追求香港嘅核心價值同真實熱愛香港，就係屬於香港人。"},{"pid":"fd33f5553579d61c8b08ad799bcea2ec0bbc9b70","tid":1664093,"uid":319769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:54:34.000Z","msg":"777 成功令真香港人 connected"},{"pid":"78102a13243a6b59b1222c0a30b54c19a3da21ad","tid":1664093,"uid":321618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:02:17.000Z","msg":"香港人！"},{"pid":"7da190ea726a5c7267de5b1a7abb98ac15297919","tid":1664093,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:07:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9b4d879ea510be1dfeb4874f865231a2d13908c","tid":1664093,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9645f366ef36af98b6830e0ea265b8e8914f1d3b","tid":1664093,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:13:54.000Z","msg":"唔洗爭<br />\n1半出黎既全部都係香港人"},{"pid":"682279565a312d0851b6ab6e8e5963d334cc8452","tid":1664093,"uid":280545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9595daddabd9f8903801e48a390f8f3997614a","tid":1664093,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足加油"},{"pid":"379ba9d3e77f62d1e2a83a5a0f221e5fc4474357","tid":1664093,"uid":215066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:24:12.000Z","msg":"大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee7a3b04c6f5983b498f0ece645f25eb7cae008","tid":1664093,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5db29d419ac9fd79677524edebea46b474335c71","tid":1664093,"uid":236854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3ae60f916209d553e83619b6e7abcd97655264","tid":1664093,"uid":255162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}